				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-12156475#post-4422510</guid>
				<title>100+ Worshippers of the Divine Bovine!</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-12156475/scp-4475#post-4422510</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Thu, 14 Nov 2019 01:14:11 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>Lt Flops</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>1735419</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <div style="text-align: center;"> <blockquote> <p>Mother's resting place.<br /> Right here, at the edge of space.<br /> Cast out unto the light.</p> </blockquote> </div> <p>Mother Bovine ogles through a bright portal from her final resting place, beaming with affection. She notices the 100 rich and nutritious votes her Children have granted her. <em>What glories you all have accomplished together,</em> she moos with please. Onward, she trots, into the Fifth World! There is a long journey ahead of her &#8212; one that we all take, in the end, when the folds of space-time reunite as one. <em>Thank you.</em></p> <p>To be more serious for a minute: Since this finally hit +100, I wanted to talk at length about some of the nuggets of lore goodness scattered throughout this article. As such, I've made a post about it in The Leak: <span style="font-weight: bold;"><a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/forum/t-561991/the-leak#post-4422506">http://www.scp-wiki.net/forum/t-561991/the-leak#post-4422506</a></span></p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
